H0.text: Small intestine is the digestive system organ of which the ileum is the last part.

H1.text: Stomach is the digestive system organ of which the ileum is the last part.

H2.text: Esophagus is the digestive system organ of which the ileum is the last part.

H3.text: The large intestine is the digestive system organ of which the ileum is the last part.

A4.text: The ileum: The final section of the small intestine.

A5.text: The ileum joins to the cecum of the large intestine at the ileocecal junction.
